steps.name: Creating All Six Item: Freestyle Project, Pipeline,Multi-configuration Project, Folder, Multibranch Pipeline,Organization Folder
Create Freestyle project with valid random name and return to dashboard
Switch to the side menu
Click 'New Item' on the Side Menu
Input the New Item name: UN1AJnLK8yn4Ub3
Select 'Freestyle project' type on NewItemPage
Click 'OK' button
Click 'Save' button on the configuration page
Switch to header
Click on 'Jenkins' name icon on the header
Create new pipeline project with valid random name 'lxJmvOwYzH3QbTo' and return to dashboard
Switch to the side menu
Click 'New Item' on the Side Menu
Input the New Item name: lxJmvOwYzH3QbTo
Select 'Pipeline' project type
Click 'OK' button
Click 'Save' button on the configuration page
Switch to header
Click on 'Jenkins' name icon on the header
Create Multi-configuration project with valid random name and return to dashboard
Switch to the side menu
Click 'New Item' on the Side Menu
Input the New Item name: LETs85clllBOZbA
Select 'Multi-configuration project' type
Click 'OK' button
Click 'Save' button on the configuration page
Switch to header
Click on 'Jenkins' name icon on the header
Create new Folder with valid random name and return to dashboard
Switch to the side menu
Click 'New Item' on the Side Menu
Input the New Item name: 32eOZmPjB335QJR
Select 'Folder' type
Click 'OK' button
Click 'Save' button on the configuration page
Switch to header
Click on 'Jenkins' name icon on the header
Create new MultibranchPipeline project with valid random name and return to dashboard
Switch to the side menu
Click 'New Item' on the Side Menu
Input the New Item name: 8ybqVXvOCAeju41
Select 'Multibranch Pipeline' item
Click 'OK' button
Click 'Save' button on the configuration page
Switch to header
Click on 'Jenkins' name icon on the header
Create new Organization folder with valid random name and return to dashboard
Switch to the side menu
Click 'New Item' on the Side Menu
Input the New Item name: 2d8rVfmMN13JqZ7
Select 'Organization folder' item
Click 'OK' button
Click 'Save' button on the configuration page
Switch to header
Click on 'Jenkins' name icon on the header
Switch to the side menu
Click on 'My Views' link on the side menu
Click on the new view icon on the 'My Views' Page
Set view name 'vSbbzHw7akJPJ62' in New View From my Views Page
Select list view type in New View From my Views Page
Click on 'Create Button'
Add jobs to list view into Edit List View Page
